  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>。現時加國北部三個地區（育空、西北地區和努拿烏特）均沒有地區銷售稅<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.taxtips.ca/pst/pstrates.htm |title=Canadian Tax and Financial Information: PST Rates |accessdate=2009-12-25 |archive-date=2010-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305233052/http://www.taxtips.ca/pst/pstrates.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

